variables.description:
The variables definition are the part that looks like task(from: $startTime, to: $endTime) in the query. 
 It works just like the argument definitions for a function in a typed language. These variables are applicable only for persisted queries that has these variables. An example of persisted query with variables - {
  task (from: $startTime, to: $endTime, filter: {
    and : [
      {channelType : {equals: telephony}}
     ]
  } , pagination: {cursor:"0"}) {
      tasks {
        id
        channelType
      }
  }
}
